<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Document</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/signup.css">
</head>
<body>
    
    <div class="main">
    <h1>Instagram</h1>
    <p id="sign_up">Sign up to see photos and videos from your friends.</p>
    <button>Log in with Facebook</button>
    <p>OR</p>
    <form action="/users/signup" method="POST">
        <div>
        <input type="number" placeholder="Mobile number" name="mobile number" required>
        </div>
        <br>
        <div>
            <input type="text" placeholder="Full name" name="fullName" required>
        </div>
        <br>
        <div>
            <input type="email" placeholder="email" name="email" required>
        </div>
        <br>
        <div>
            <input type="password" placeholder="Password" name="password" required>
        </div>   
        <p>People who use our service may have uploaded your contact information to instagram.<a href="#">Learn more</a></p>
        
        <p>By singing up ,you agree to our <a href="#">Terms</a>.<a href="#">Privacy Policy</a>and <a href="#">Cookies policy</a></p>
        <button>Sign up</button>
        </form> 
    </div> 
    
</body>
</html>